#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:2 dd7a13a2382444669dffdeec5dd76a2d
msgid "使用说明"
msgstr "Instructions"

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:4 b4cba23036ce44ae95633dc95a6cef11
msgid ""
"本节为 AiThinker-FAQ 的使用说明。“问题查找”旨在帮助您快速了解该网站的搜索方法"
"及分类框架，节省问题查找时间。"
msgstr ""
"This section provides instructions for using AiThinker-FAQ. “Question "
"Search” is intended to help you quickly understand the search methods and "
"category framework of this website, saving time when looking for answers."

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:7 4e8907db49894dbcac2677f18586070d
msgid "搜索问题技巧"
msgstr "Tips for Searching Questions"

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:9 24e53091fe294a2a89bdc19e18ff3b1c
msgid "目前可以归纳出以下 2 种搜索问题的技巧："
msgstr "Currently, the following two search techniques can be summarized:"

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:11
#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:15 93fe52e9554540eea5d83d676c63b543
#: 4fb7aa59ec4e4557873c96b8af5fd8e3
msgid "搜索关键词"
msgstr "Search by Keywords"

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:12
#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:25 ef7e916f5d204e10a8845dee0ba5fc79
#: ece9c577c96b437eb5deaf2d9c7c53d1
msgid "排除某个关键词"
msgstr "Exclude a Certain Keyword"

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:17 6bc758148d744a6d9aa1d2ae789b2214
msgid "将问题中的关键词提取出来并搜索它们，此时搜索结果会得到最匹配的结果。"
msgstr ""
"Extract the keywords from the question and search for them. The search "
"results will then return the most relevant matches."

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:20 4eea11e1319b49be991f7b0f6ce49272
msgid "比如问题为：``Ai-WB2-12F 的 Bluetooth LE 吞吐量是多少？``"
msgstr "For example, if the question is: ``What is the Bluetooth LE throughput of Ai-WB2-12F?``"

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:22 418f6cf043e640b6bae64969655142e5
msgid "此时搜索：``Ai-WB2-12F``、``BLE`` 和 ``吞吐量`` 等关键字为宜。"
msgstr "In this case, it is recommended to search for keywords such as ``Ai-WB2-12F``, ``BLE``, and ``throughput``."

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:27 d924381104cc45fb98514d16a6763b62
msgid ""
"在搜索内容中添加一个标识符 ``-``, 格式为： ``关键词  -排除关键词``。此时搜索"
"结果不会出现有排除关键词的结果。"
msgstr ""
"Add the identifier ``-`` to the search content in the following format: "
"``keyword -excluded_keyword``. In this case, search results containing the "
"excluded keyword will not appear."

#: ../source/docs/instruction/index.rst:29 02031687935040aab9b786263b30e5cd
msgid ""
"比如搜索：``Ai-WB2-12F -ble``。任何搜索结果中有 ``ble`` 的结果将会被过滤。"
msgstr ""
"For example, search for: ``Ai-WB2-12F -ble``. Any search result containing "
"``ble`` will be filtered out."

